parameters:
You're the dancer for today at the illegal bar, huh? Your
face looks young, but your body is perfect.
Clea: Is it acceptable that I passed?

Bouncer at the illegal bar: 'Hey, wait a minute! Are you
planning to bring that stupidly big sword in too!?'  Note:
The translation assumes that the speaker is referring to
Clea's sword.
Clea: Yes, is there a problem...?

Bouncer at the illegal bar: 'Of course! We'll hold onto it
here, so lend it to us.'

Clea: This is a dance prop. Using this is the Fotizona-
style dance.

The bouncer at the illegal bar: 'The city is crazy, huh...
I'll make a special exception and allow it, but please don't
cause any trouble, okay?'

Bouncer at the illegal bar: 'This isn't a place for a young
lady to come. I don't know who persuaded you, but go home.'

Mage Relm: Please don't treat me like a child! I belong to
the Magic Academy! I may be a genius!

The bouncer at the illegal bar: 'Geez, those kind of lies
sound childish. But I guess even a dancer like you can be
appreciated once in a while... You can go!'

Mage Relm (It seems like I can enter without arousing
suspicion... but I'm not satisfied with that!)

Illegal bar bouncer: So you're today's dancer, huh? Your
body may be big for a woman, but it seems like it'll stand
out on stage.
Thief Nora: Hii, I-I'll do my best...

Illegal bar bouncer: Did someone sell you out? I feel sorry
for you, but we're also running a business, so please give
up.
Thief Nora: Y-Yes... then, excuse me.

Illegal bar bouncer: Sorry, but please leave your weapons
behind. Bringing weapons into the bar is prohibited.
Thief Nora: Eh, ah, yes... I'm sorry...

Thief Nora (Ugh... I handed it over without resistance... I
wonder if it'll be okay...)
Illegal bar bouncer: Oh, so you're today's dancer...!?
Priestess Sophia: Hic... Umm, are you okay?

Illegal bar bouncer: I've been a bouncer for a long time...
but it's the first time I've been so captivated that I
stumbled over my words.

Illegal bar bouncer: Don't come out too much on stage, as
excited customers might cause a ruckus.

Priestess Sophia: Thank you for your advice. Well then,
please let me through.

Illegal bar bouncer: Today's customers are lucky... I want
to see too.

Illegal bar bouncer: If you want a job other than being a
dancer, talk to the bar's Vreppo.
